%h1 Writing Sample

%p In 500 words or fewer, explain a complex topic from your area of expertise.

%p Writing should be original to this application. Citations are not necessary but welcome if they feel appropriate. Use Markdown formatting (<a href='http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax'>http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax</a>) as needed.

%p Post the text as a private gist on <a href='https://gist.github.com/' target='_blank'>https://gist.github.com/</a> and submit the URL below.

%p Please ensure that the document contains **NO OTHER FORMATTING** than markdown. In other words, we do not want to see any

%ul
  %li HTML
  %li RTF
  %li MSWord formatting

%p Also make sure that the text does not require horizontal scrolling to read. Break your lines at 78 columns if you see that the text does scroll.

%h2 URL to Gist

= form_for :essay, url: step_essay_path, method: :put do |f|
  - if @essay.errors.any?
    %p= @essay.errors.full_messages
  = f.label :url
  = f.text_field :url
  = f.submit 'save'

